 "name": "RPlog_Retribution_-_Jedi_and_Sith_Duel",
 "title": "Retribution: Jedi and Sith Duel",
 "summary": "In the acid rain and ruin of war-torn Coruscant, a battered Luke Skywalker, dust-caked and tattered, rouses from a meditative trance near the shattered Senate building as a squad of blood-pauldroned 65th Legion stormtroopers fan out through the courtyard. There the Jedi Master confronts the Sith Warlord Korolov in a climactic duel amid the rubble of the capital. The desperate clash of lightsaber and dark-side power forms a centerpiece of the wider battle of retribution, Luke standing against the Sith in the heart of the fallen Republic seat.",
